nodes.text: Zerala Dinn was a Force-sensitive human male from the planet Naboo who worked as a con artist operating in Theed. Dinn formed a partnership with Blaise Zirkonn, another Force-sensitive who served as an agent of the Galactic Empire's Inquisitorius. Zirkonn became Dinn's agent on Theed and part of the Inquisitorius.
